body:
Well today is the day I received my first Honour Capsule from the Honour System  and honestly it was a surprise that I did not even expect.
up till today I had gotten a few keys here and there for my honour title, to receive an experience that not only felt like a payed item but also contained better items than one; well it put a smile on my face.
so thank you to who ever came up with that idea at Riot you the real mvp.{{sticker:slayer-pantheon-thumbs}}
